title: 2021 CFB Pick Em Week 10
description:
El Pres, Big Cat & Rico are back for another week of picks. Rico's ambition gets put into question after not being at Sunday's stream. Also we react to the first CFB playoff rankings.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
